<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>New Advisor Created</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f3f4f6; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color: #1f2937;">
    <div style="padding: 32px 16px;">
      <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; border-collapse: separate; border-spacing: 0;">
        <tr>
          <td style="background-color: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 22px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 20px 54px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);">
            <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse: collapse;">
              <tr>
                <td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eef2ff 0%, #f0fdf4 100%); padding: 30px 34px;">
                  <p style="margin: 0; color: #6366f1; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;">New Advisor Alert</p>
                  <h1 style="margin: 10px 0 6px; font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.35; font-weight: 700; color: #111827;">New advisor profile created: {{advisorName}}</h1>
                  <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.6;">
                    A new advisor has successfully created their profile on the Advisor Chooser platform.
                  </p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td style="padding: 26px 32px 24px;">
                  <div style="background-color: #f9fafb; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 18px; padding: 22px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #6366f1; font-weight: 700;">Advisor Details</p>
                    <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 18px; font-size: 14px; color: #1f2937; line-height: 1.7;">
                      <li><strong>Company Name:</strong> {{advisorCompanyName}}</li>
                      <li><strong>Email:</strong> {{advisorEmail}}</li>
                      <li><strong>Phone:</strong> {{advisorPhone}}</li>
                      <li><strong>Website:</strong> {{advisorWebsite}}</li>
                      <li><strong>Years of Experience:</strong> {{advisorExperience}} years</li>
                      <li><strong>Number of Transactions:</strong> {{advisorTransactions}}</li>
                      <li><strong>Industries:</strong> {{advisorIndustries}}</li>
                      <li><strong>Geographies:</strong> {{advisorGeographies}}</li>
                      <li><strong>Revenue Range:</strong> ${{advisorRevenueMin}} - ${{advisorRevenueMax}} {{advisorCurrency}}</li>
                      <li><strong>Worked with CIM Amplify:</strong> {{workedWithCimamplify}}</li>
                      <li><strong>Accepting Leads:</strong> {{sendLeads}}</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>

                  <div style="background-color: #eef2ff; border: 1px solid #c7d2fe; border-radius: 18px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <h2 style="margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 18px; color: #111827;">Profile Summary</h2>
                    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.7;">{{advisorDescription}}</p>
                  </div>

                  <div style="background-color: #f9fafb; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 18px; padding: 22px;">
                    <h3 style="margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 16px; color: #111827;">Next Steps</h3>
                    <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 18px; font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.7;">
                      <li>Review the advisor profile for completeness and accuracy</li>
                      <li>Verify advisor credentials and experience claims</li>
                      <li>Approve or request modifications to the profile</li>
                      <li>Add the advisor to the active matching pool if approved</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>

                  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 22px 0 10px;">
                    <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 26px; border-radius: 999px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5, #7c3aed); color: #ffffff; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;">View Admin Dashboard</a>
                  </div>

                  <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center;">Questions? Email support@advisorchooser.com anytime.</p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <p style="margin: 22px auto 0; max-width: 680px; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center;">
        This is an automated notification from the Advisor Chooser platform. You received this because you are the project owner.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>